summary:
Ambitious international account manager with a passion for research and a lot of intercultural experience, well-developed conceptual thinking and analytical skills. My customers describe me as engaging, trustworthy, dedicated, driven, result-oriented and proactive. I would like to invest the knowledge, skills and competences that I have acquired during my studies and work in an international company. 

I am fluent in English, Spanish, Romanian, Russian, Dutch and I have moderate abilities in Italian and French.
